  <CloudDivider fillClass="fill-[var(--color-mint-100)]" />
  <CaptionedBlock heading="How Every Puppy Is Checked Before You Take It Home" imageAlt="Puppy receiving a health check" imageSrc={healthCheck} variant="mid">
    <p>
      Every puppy is health-checked before going home, and vaccinated in line with the{' '}
      <a href="https://avs.nparks.gov.sg/businesses/veterinarians/guidelines-for-veterinarians/sg-vaccination-guidelines-for-dogs-and-cats/" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">Singapore Vaccination Guidelines for Dogs and Cats</a>,
      jointly published by AVS and the Singapore Veterinary Association. Core vaccination protects against canine parvovirus and distemper, two of the most serious risks to a young puppy.
    </p>
    <p>We mention this once, plainly, because it matters, not because we want you worried every time you read our site.</p>
  </CaptionedBlock>
  <CloudDivider fillClass="fill-[var(--color-mint-100)]" flip />

  <div id="reviews" class="scroll-mt-40">
