  <CaptionedBlock heading="Our Care and Support Promise" imageAlt="Nelson and Kim checking on a puppy at the shop" imageSrc={careSupport} imagePosition="left" variant="card">
    <p>Buying the puppy isn't where our part ends. If you have any questions about caring for your puppy after you bring them home, our customer service is free, and it doesn't stop after the first week.</p>
    <p>Most questions are already answered before you need to ask them: Nelson and Kim walk through how to use and care for your puppy with every one of the 30 starter-kit items, in person, before you leave with your puppy.</p>
    <p>If your puppy falls sick within the first 5 days of coming home, bring them back to us and we'll nurse them ourselves.</p>
