    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-5 sm:px-8 -mt-6 pb-10">
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-cream-600)]">
        The ICA reported a 33% decrease in animal smuggling cases in 2025, but unlicensed sources remain high risk: puppies often carry undetected parvovirus, unvaccinated puppies can mean $5,000+ in vet bills within days, and there's no recourse if the seller disappears. Our approach is transparent, verifiable, and accountable.
      </p>
